Text: Confirmation of am meeting at KMV in San Francisco Cc Mr Kaminski Thank you for your phone messages confirming that you and Mr Bill Bradford will be meeting with Mr Robert Rudy Managing Director Head of Client Service this Monday March th from am pm We are looking forward to seeing you and hopefully well even have some sunny weather for you Attached are the directions to our office Please be sure to note that our dress code is business casual so please do not feel obligated to wear a suit and tie Directions to KMVdoc Please let me know if you have any questions Sincerely Kristina J Wun Marketing Coordinator KMV LLC Montgomery Street Suite San Francisco California direct line general line fax line Directions to KMVdoc
